    "For a current overview, see for instance Mehrabi et al. (2022) or Gallegos et al. (2024).",
    "Blinkered chunk effect (BCE)",
    "A plain vanilla RAG implementation is limited in terms of a comprehensive understanding of extensive data.",
    "New approaches such as RAPTOR (Sarthi et al. 2024) are required to reduce this issue.",
    "The effectiveness of a RAG architecture depends on how effectively the retrieval mechanism works."
